Hey, did you and Dad
feel that earthquake?

07:48.958 --> 07:50.363
Are you guys all right?

07:50.388 --> 07:53.046
Oh, we're fine.
The house shook a little bit.

07:53.071 --> 07:56.025
I think your dad thought
he was on a roller coaster.

07:56.050 --> 07:57.207
Are you okay?

07:57.209 --> 07:59.572
