08:49.770 --> 08:51.963
- <i>Zoey?</i>
- Uh, yeah, yeah. I'm here.

08:51.988 --> 08:56.071
I'm sorry. I'm just, um, feeling
a little strange right now.

08:56.096 --> 08:57.878
Well, take the rest of the day off.

08:57.903 --> 09:00.517
<i>Really, go home.
You need to take care of yourself.</i>

