33:47.018 --> 33:50.086
♪ It's hard to take courage ♪

33:50.111 --> 33:53.079
♪ In a world full of people ♪

33:53.104 --> 33:55.673
♪ You can lose sight of it all ♪

33:55.698 --> 34:00.313
