can make you feel so small ♪

34:00.338 --> 34:03.372
♪ But I see your true colors ♪

34:03.397 --> 34:05.397
♪ Shining through ♪

34:05.434 --> 34:08.969
♪ I see your true colors ♪

34:08.994 --> 34:11.514
