34:11.540 --> 34:14.304
♪ So don't be afraid ♪

34:14.330 --> 34:16.837
♪ To let them show ♪

34:16.862 --> 34:19.813
♪ Your true colors ♪

34:19.838 --> 34:22.304
♪ True colors ♪

34:22.330 --> 34:26.321
♪ Are beautiful ♪

