♪ Show me a smile then ♪

34:41.135 --> 34:43.290
♪ Don't be unhappy ♪

34:43.315 --> 34:45.748
♪ Can't remember when ♪

34:45.773 --> 34:48.897
♪ I last saw you laughing ♪

