or real tragedy in her life,

36:45.841 --> 36:49.285
so I'm not sure she
really, really relates,

36:49.859 --> 36:51.808
at least not the way you do.

36:52.486 --> 36:54.739
You gave me good advice. It's just...

36:54.764 --> 36:57.255
hard when the two sides
aren't connecting.

36:57.350 --> 36:58.647
And sometimes it feels like we're in

36:58.671 --> 37:01.905
