40:53.656 --> 40:56.037
Is it weird that I'm now
a little intimated by you?

40:56.062 --> 40:57.084
Oh, please.

40:57.109 --> 40:59.522
So, first day, how you feeling?

40:59.547 --> 41:01.537
Really good, actually.

41:01.562 --> 41:03.217
You know, I just want to tell you

41:03.242 --> 41:05.514
