been through all of this, Max.

41:05.539 --> 41:06.850
It's just been really comforting

41:06.875 --> 41:09.616
to know that I have you
as, like, my rock.

41:09.641 --> 41:12.381
And crazy thing is,
I haven't even told you

41:12.406 --> 41:14.240
